@toollean v0.1
@tool table-image-generator
@desc Generate clean table images from data. Perfect for Discord/Telegram where ASCII tables look broken. Supports dark/light mode, custom styling, and auto-sizing. No Puppeteer required. Companion to chart-image skill.
@source /data/workspace/skills/table-image-generator/SKILL.md
@example
  > cd /data/clawd/skills/table-image/scripts && npm install
@example
  > node table.mjs \
